00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:43,410
By fifty—

255
00:22:43,410 --> 00:22:47,420
No, Sister Li. Isn't fifty percent a little too high?

256
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:51,230
 Little sister, many people are fighting for your house.

257
00:22:51,230 --> 00:22:54,460
 I saw that life isn't easy for you so I never rented it to anyone else.

258
00:22:54,460 --> 00:22:58,140
 If you're tight on money, why don't you make some room for others?

259
00:22:58,140 --> 00:23:02,170
I can't, Sister Li. I'll send it to you. I'll send it right now.

260
00:23:02,170 --> 00:23:04,250
Bye, Sister Li.

261
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:09,230

262
00:23:09,230 --> 00:23:11,520

263
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:15,080

264
00:23:15,080 --> 00:23:19,790
Eight, eight, eight. This number is quite auspicious.

265
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:27,250
Look, I really don't have money.

266
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:29,660
