Can people really live here?

294
00:25:39,050 --> 00:25:40,800
What do you mean by "can people really live here"?

295
00:25:40,800 --> 00:25:43,270
I've lived here for several years already.

296
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:44,560
Then which floor do you live on?

297
00:25:44,560 --> 00:25:47,680
The second floor. Right there.

298
00:25:56,510 --> 00:25:58,130
Careful.

299
00:25:58,720 --> 00:26:00,330
Let's go.

300
00:26:02,420 --> 00:26:04,340
You don't have an elevator?

301
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:05,950
We only have stairs.

302
00:26:05,950 --> 00:26:09,400
Moreover, it's only the second floor. It will be fine if I help you up.

303
00:26:27,320 --> 00:26:28,990
What happened?

304
00:26:29,490 --> 00:26:31,730
