What is that?

312
00:28:10,950 --> 00:28:13,630
This is something that all cups have after being used for a long time.

313
00:28:13,630 --> 00:28:15,200
Probably water marks.

314
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:17,550
It's fine. You won't die. Drink it.

315
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:39,920
It's clean now.

316
00:28:42,490 --> 00:28:44,010
Where do I sleep?

317
00:28:44,010 --> 00:28:47,530
I can't sleep on the couch, right? I'm still a patient.

318
00:28:48,840 --> 00:28:51,530
I'll give you a tour of the bedroom.

319
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:19,660
You draw comics?

320
00:29:19,660 --> 00:29:22,330
I doodle when I'm bored.

321
00:29:22,330 --> 00:29:24,060
I'm just a courier.

322
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:27,850
Sit anywhere. I will tidy up this place for you.

323
00:29:58,860 --> 00:30:00,530
Don't touch.

324
00:30:02,010 --> 00:30:03,810
Is that your mom?

325
00:30:05,130 --> 00:30:07,520
Does it have anything to do with you?

326
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:09,380
Just asking.

327
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:12,570
I'm telling you, you can sleep in my bedroom,

328
00:30:12,570 --> 00:30:14,900
but you can't touch anything in my bedroom.

329
00:30:14,900 --> 00:30:18,470
These are all my treasures. I bought them with my savings.

330
00:30:18,470 --> 00:30:20,330
You hear me?

331
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:24,350
No need. I will sleep on the couch.

332
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:39,370
There's no air conditioning in the house, only a fan.

333
00:30:39,370 --> 00:30:43,890
If you think it's too hot, your only choice is to deal with it.

334
00:31:05,730 --> 00:31:07,630
What is it?

335
00:31:07,630 --> 00:31:10,630
The couch can't be placed under the fan.

336
00:31:10,630 --> 00:31:13,730
Why? Are there any Feng Shui specifications for that?

337
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:17,300
It's too dangerous.

338
00:31:17,300 --> 00:31:19,460
How is it dangerous?

339
00:31:22,630 --> 00:31:25,230
Either you move the couch...

340
00:31:25,230 --> 00:31:27,860
- Cou— 
 - ...or...

341
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:32,500
if you don't mind, I can sleep in the same room with you.

342
00:31:38,230 --> 00:31:44,140
You... You look proper enough. You aren't going to do anything to me, right?

343
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:46,200
Not necessarily.

344
00:31:47,630 --> 00:31:50,230
- I'm warning you— 
 - I'm also warning you.

345
00:31:50,230 --> 00:31:53,100
You still owe me ¥280,000.

346
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:54,600
Not ¥280,000.

347
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:57,560
It's ¥272,000.

348
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:08,500
The water bill, room and board,

349
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:12,270
the tricycle, and the costs of my care.

350
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:16,340
Adding all of this up, it's about ¥8,000.

351
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:20,600
So now, I still owe you ¥272,000.

352
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:25,590
So was your service more expensive or this shabby house of yours?

353
00:32:25,590 --> 00:32:29,470
How is my house shabby? I even have a luxurious, big bathtub.

354
00:32:29,470 --> 00:32:33,330
Furthermore, my service is 24 hours

355
00:32:33,330 --> 00:32:36,900
of personal service. This is considered cheap.

356
00:32:38,890 --> 00:32:41,210
How personal?

357
00:32:45,120 --> 00:32:48,030
It's... within three meters,

358
00:32:48,030 --> 00:32:50,290
and further than one meter.

359
00:32:54,730 --> 00:32:56,240
Okay.

360
00:32:56,850 --> 00:32:58,630
Then, listen carefully.

361
00:32:58,630 --> 00:33:00,820
I only drink mineral water. I only use 100% cotton towels.

362
00:33:00,820 --> 00:33:03,740
The lights must be out in the living room by 11:00 p.m. You're not allowed to bother me after that.

363
00:33:03,740 --> 00:33:06,820
I've only thought of these. I will add on when I think of the rest.

364
00:33:07,580 --> 00:33:09,800
Why does your brain work so well even though you've lost your memory?

365
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:12,780
I will emphasize this once more. I have a temporary memory gap.

366
00:33:12,780 --> 00:33:17,090
Not dementia. Those who can't do anything after losing their memories only belong in TV dramas.

367
00:33:17,890 --> 00:33:20,630
Go, move the couch for me.

368
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:39,290

369
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:43,920
Why are there still so few clicks?

370
00:35:26,430 --> 00:35:29,870
 You can eat cup noodles at noon, a very good deal.

371
00:35:30,810 --> 00:35:32,310
 Breakfast is on the table.

372
00:35:32,310 --> 00:35:35,130
 Your mineral water is in the fridge.

373
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:39,590

374
00:35:42,740 --> 00:35:45,740
 Second-hand clothes were put under the couch.

375
00:36:04,770 --> 00:36:07,680

376
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:24,090
How come there's suddenly a fire at house 208?

377
00:36:24,090 --> 00:36:26,280
I heard the microwave caught on fire.

378
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:29,090
- 208? 
 - Yes.

379
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:35,380
What happened to my house?

380
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:37,150
In the future, when using appliances, you must be careful.

381
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:39,940
Don't put metal in the microwave.

382
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:43,600
Microwave...

383
00:37:08,930 --> 00:37:11,880
You've never used a microwave at your house, right?

384
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:15,970
If you have nothing to do, go take a stroll outside. Don't mess up the house.

385
00:37:15,970 --> 00:37:18,190
This is all money.

386
00:37:28,040 --> 00:37:31,390
Damage of appliances, ¥600.

387
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,790

388
00:37:37,970 --> 00:37:39,300
My phone number.

389
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:42,950
If you run into trouble, call me, but I hope that you have no reason to call.

390
00:37:42,950 --> 00:37:44,650
Okay?

391
00:37:55,420 --> 00:37:56,680
Hello?

392
00:37:56,680 --> 00:38:00,270
 Anxin, your older brother broke the beer bottles in my store. You should come over quickly.

393
00:38:00,270 --> 00:38:01,790
Brother?

394
00:38:01,790 --> 00:38:04,080
Look at what my beer bottles have become.

395
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:06,560
- Sorry, sir. 
 - The delivery just arrived.

396
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:08,070
This beer is very expensive.

397
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:10,910
Your brother broke the whole crate.

398
00:38:10,910 --> 00:38:12,640
I'm going to lose a lot of money.

399
00:38:12,640 --> 00:38:14,760
That's all I have in cash right now.

400
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:18,120
When I get my paycheck, I will send the rest to you immediately, okay?

401
00:38:18,120 --> 00:38:21,100
- Seriously. 
 - I told you to go take a stroll outside.

402
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:23,860
I didn't tell you to go out and take money for a walk.

403
00:38:28,730 --> 00:38:32,410
- Hello? 
   - My son was scared into tears by your husband.

404
00:38:32,410 --> 00:38:34,310
Sorry, Little Kid.

405
00:38:34,310 --> 00:38:36,170
You're Gu Anxin?

406
00:38:36,170 --> 00:38:38,550
Why is someone so old taking toys from a kid?

407
00:38:38,550 --> 00:38:41,260
Can you watch your husband? Seriously.

408
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,840
I'm really sorry.

