454
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:57,330
So, you're saying that there are 84 cockroaches currently in my house?

455
00:41:57,330 --> 00:41:59,110
That's right.

456
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:10,810
I'm telling you... You still haven't realized the severity of this issue.

